tep #10: Outline Your Communication Plan\">Step #10: Outline Your Communication Plan<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/digital-trends\/communication-strategy\/#Download-FREE-Brand-Communication-Strategy-Template-2\" title=\"Download FREE Brand Communication Strategy Template\">Download FREE Brand Communication Strategy Template<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-20\" href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/digital-trends\/communication-strategy\/#Communication-Strategy-Takeaways\" title=\"Communication Strategy Takeaways\">Communication Strategy Takeaways<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What-Is-A-Brand-Communication-Strategy\"><\/span>What Is A Brand Communication Strategy?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A brand communication strategy, also known as a communication strategy, is a&nbsp;comprehensive plan that helps you profile your audiences and <strong>craft compelling and consistent messaging that will resonate with them.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Typically, you can request a brand communication strategy when you utilize <a href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/branding-agency\/digital-branding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">branding services<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your brand communication strategy should answer three key questions about your brand:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>What<\/strong> is your brand and the message behind it?<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Who<\/strong> are you attempting to reach with your brand?<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>How<\/strong> will you reach them?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In other words, it defines the three most important aspects of your brand:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Messaging<\/strong>: The unique value proposition of your brand that differentiates it from its competitors<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Target audience:<\/strong> The group of customers that the messaging will resonate with<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Channels<\/strong>: The mix of tools and outlets via which the messaging will be communicated to the target audience<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n    <div class=\"cta-custom-box\">\n                    <span style='color: #008dde;'>Schedule a consultation with our branding strategy experts<\/span>\n                <a class=\"arrow-right black\" href=\"\/contact\/\"  rel=\"noopener\">\n            Set Up A Consultation        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FREE-Communication-Strategy-Example-Template-What-Does-A-Communication-Strategy-Include\"><\/span>FREE Communication Strategy Example &amp; Template: What Does A Communication Strategy Include?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Developing a digital communication strategy is a lengthy process that can be disorienting. <strong>That\u2019s why we summarized this article into a template that you can use for reference.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><style type=\"text\/css\">\r\n\t\t#dae-shortcode7505-download-wrapper {\r\n\t\t\tbackground: #454ca0 !important;\r\n\t\t\tbackground-attachment: scroll !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t#dae-shortcode7505-download-wrapper .dae-shortcode-download-file-image {\r\n\t\t\twidth: 80% !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t#dae-shortcode7505-download-wrapper.dae-shortcode-download-wrapper-wide .dae-shortcode-download-file-image {\r\n\t\t\twidth: 40% !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t#dae-shortcode7505-download-wrapper .dae-shortcode-download-title {\r\n\t\t\tfont-size: 25px !important;\r\n\t\t\tfont-family: Open Sans, sans-serif !important;\r\n\t\t\tcolor: #ffffff !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t#dae-shortcode7505-download-wrapper .dae-shortcode-download-text {\r\n\t\t\tfont-size: 16px !important;\r\n\t\t\tfont-family: Open Sans, sans-serif !important;\r\n\t\t\tcolor: #ffffff !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n